<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gestione Distributori</title>
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #333333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1MCIgaGVpZ2h0PSI1MCI+CiAgPGNpcmNsZSBjeD0iMjUiIGN5PSIyNSIgcj0iMiIgZmlsbD0icmdiYSgyNTUsMjU1LDI1NSwwLjEpIi8+Cjwvc3ZnPg==');
            opacity: 0.05;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-shadow: none;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            max-width: 600px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            opacity: 0.9;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #1976D2;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .material-icons {
            vertical-align: middle;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        .coffee-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2196F3;
            background: rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            animation: float 3s infinite ease-in-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        
        .steam {
            position: absolute;
            width: 2px;
            height: 20px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            animation: rise 2s infinite ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .steam:nth-child(1) { left: 50%; animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .steam:nth-child(2) { left: 55%; animation-delay: 0.6s; }
        .steam:nth-child(3) { left: 45%; animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        
        @keyframes rise {
            0% { transform: translateY(0) scaleX(1); opacity: 0; }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px) scaleX(1.5); opacity: 0.5; }
            100% { transform: translateY(-40px) scaleX(1); opacity: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="steam-container">
            <div class="steam"></div>
            <div class="steam"></div>
            <div class="steam"></div>
        </div>
        <i class="material-icons coffee-icon">local_cafe</i>
        <h1>Gestione Distributori Automatici</h1>
        <p>Monitora, gestisci e ottimizza la tua rete di distributori automatici di bevande calde in tempo reale. 
           Accedi alla piattaforma per visualizzare statistiche, ricavi e stato delle tue macchinette.</p>
        <a href="/istituti" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
            <i class="material-icons">dashboard</i>
            Accedi al Dashboard
        </a>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>